Holy shit!  That&#39;s insane!  Well, if people are paying for it, then more power to &#39;em.  

I always liked doing traditional EVP and still do on investigations, but it doesn&#39;t hold a candle to the box research.  I&#39;ve been wanting to try the Raudive method with a germanium diode.  Radio shack only carries silicon, so I&#39;ll have to order the germanium and give it a shot.  

I understand having to sell things to pay the bills.  I&#39;ve had to part with guitars and other equipment in the past.  The necessities always come first.

Steve, I&#39;m glad you&#39;re enjoying the standard EVP work so much.  It&#39;s good to find something to help keep things fresh.

Jeremy

